  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5155448/" class="title-link">good：相关文献详尽；bad：中世纪部分打马过桥</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5155448"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2521369/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2521369-10.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2521369/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">李大卫</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-11-05"
      class="main-meta">2011-11-05 03:23:34</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5155448_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  最大的好处是文献列举详尽，给后来者一个很好的“哲学地形图”。  缺憾是中世纪部分有打马过桥（不够细致，进展过快）的感觉，推荐给初涉猎者，因为依个人经验，初涉猎者不会对中世纪思想过多关注，此书的劣处反而成了好处。  

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
